sec.p:
To have quantitative insights of the blue light-inducible/repressible system behavior, a kinetic model based on ordinary differential equations were developed. The model was developed and simulated using MATLAB Simulink to investigate the mRNA synthesis rate of the two light-dependant promoter systems, mRNA abundance and fluorescent protein production as a function of time and illumination conditions. The experiment data in Figure 4 together with literature data was first used to parameterize the model. The ODE equations and the detailed derivation of the model are described below:
